snippet.title: Ghost Bros Teaser Trailer (early development game)
snippet.description:
Check out our Kickstarter for early access! https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/ghostbros/ghost-bros?ref=59ao9g

Music by: @LoreoftheWorlds 
Voice acting by: @johnzaku , @ItsJonnyBE , @queenb3atrix 
You heard https://www.twitch.tv/rouxal and https://www.twitch.tv/chad_james pre-alpha testing!
Written and edited by: Emily

We may be playing live right now: https://www.twitch.tv/playguepals
